@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F1F8E9
skinparam classBorderColor #33691E
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Created
Created --> Delivered : cancel
Created : entry / log book
Delivered --> Reviewed : confirm
Reviewed --> Closed : approve
Reviewed : entry / log book
Closed --> Rejected : submit
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml